<preface id="preface-Reference_Guide-Introduction">
<title>About GateIn</title>

	<para>
		&PRODUCT; is the merge of two mature Java projects; JBoss Portal and eXo Portal. This new community project takes the best of both offerings and incorporates them into a single portal framework. GateIn aims at providing an intuitive user-friendly portal, and a framework to address the needs of Web 2.0 applications today.
	</para>
